    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the period in history when Rome was ruled by kings, traditionally from the founding of the city by the legendary Romulus in 753 BCE to the establishment of the Republic in 509 BCE.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere al período en historia cuando Roma fue gobernada por reyes, tradicionalmente desde la fundación de la ciudad por el legendario Rómulo en 753 a.C al establecimiento de la República en 509 a.C.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de historische periode toen Rome door koningen werd geregeerd, traditioneel gezien vanaf de stichting van de stad door de legendarische Romulus in 753 v. Chr. tot de vestiging van de Republiek in 509 v. Chr.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指稱羅馬為許多君王所統治的歷史時代，傳統而言是此時期始於傳說中的羅繆勒斯(Romulus)在西元前753年時建立羅馬城市，直至西元前509年羅馬共和國成立為止。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
